        <p class="lead">Independent living at Azalea Estates is for seniors who are fully capable of managing their own lives — but have decided there are better uses for their time than home maintenance, grocery runs, and cooking every meal.</p>
        <p>Our independent residents come and go as they please, travel when they want, and host family whenever they like. They return to a beautifully maintained apartment with dinner waiting, a full activity calendar to choose from, and a campus full of neighbors who have become genuine friends.</p>
        <p>This isn&rsquo;t a compromise. It&rsquo;s an upgrade.</p>
        <div class="signature">
