        <span class="eyebrow">Social Life</span>
        <h2>Days that feel full again.</h2>
        <p class="lead">The social calendar at Azalea Estates is one of the things independent residents mention most — not because activities are required, but because there&rsquo;s genuinely always something worth showing up for.</p>
        <p>Our full-time Activity Director builds the monthly calendar around what residents actually enjoy: excursions into Fayetteville and greater Atlanta, visits from local churches and civic groups, school children who come to spend time with residents, live entertainment, and clubs and classes that suit every interest.</p>
